languages.text: "Меня интересует главное — в тот раз обряд увенчался успехом? Ты нашел что искал?"

languages.text: 「{mf|俺|私}が知りたいのは、その儀式は成功したのかということだ。探していたものは見つかったのか？」

languages.text: “我最想了解的事情是：当时仪式成功了吗？你们找到要找的东西了吗？”
languages.original_text: "The important thing I am interested to know is, was the ritual successful that time? Did you find what you were looking for?"

traits.locale_text: “我最想了解的事情是：当时仪式成功了吗？你们找到要找的东西了吗？”

languages.text: "Was mich am meisten interessiert: War das Ritual damals erfolgreich? Habt Ihr gefunden, wonach Ihr gesucht habt?"
languages.original_text: "The important thing I am interested to know is, was the ritual successful that time? Did you find what you were looking for?"

languages.text: « Ce que j'aimerais vraiment savoir, c'est si le rituel a fonctionné. Avez-vous trouvé ce que vous cherchiez ? »
languages.original_text: "The important thing I am interested to know is, was the ritual successful that time? Did you find what you were looking for?"

languages.text: "Bilmek istediğim önemli bir ayrıntı var. O denemede ayin başarılı oldu mu? Aradığınızı bulabildiniz mi?"
